tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE IrisScanData (
  iris_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  scan_data BYTEA,
  verification_status VARCHAR(50),
  scan_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS IrisScans (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    scan_data BYTEA,
    scan_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    UNIQUE (user_id, scan_timestamp)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS VerificationProcesses (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    verification_status BOOLEAN,
    process_duration FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES IrisScans(user_id)
);
